item.title: Experimenting with things
item.description: The way this website is set up, the blog feature seems prominant. I’m not sure if that’s what I want to emphasize with it, but I guess we’ll see how it goes. For now, I’m happy that it’s working as well as it is. I might experiment with different themes going forward.
